Name: Light Fighters

Game Mechanics: 
 - Fast paced CTF/DM 
 - Set in the dark
 - 3D Multilevel maps
 - Controls (customisable)
    - wasd for up, left, down, right respectively
    - eq for pitch right, pitch left
    - shift for light on/off
    - Space to shoot
    - op for next/previous weapon
  - There is no way to speed up or slow down, each vehicle has it's own preset speed, agility/handling, weapons, ammo, light brightness
